<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MCP Access — {{projectName}}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: #1a1a2e; padding: 32px 40px; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; }
    .body { padding: 32px 40px; color: #333; }
    .body p { line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; background: #e8f0fe; color: #1a73e8; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }
    .section { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .section h3 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 15px; color: #444; }
    .section h4 { margin: 16px 0 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #555; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    .code { font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; background: #1a1a2e; color: #e2e8f0; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 13px; display: block; margin: 6px 0; overflow-x: auto; word-break: break-all; }
    .key-box { background: #fff8e1; border: 1px solid #ffe082; border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 16px 0; }
    .key-box p { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #795548; }
    .key-box .code { background: #37474f; }
    .warning { font-size: 12px; color: #e65100; margin: 6px 0 0; }
    .footer { padding: 20px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; color: #888; font-size: 12px; }
    .footer a { color: #1a73e8; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>emergent memory</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi there,</p>
      <p>
        <strong>{{senderName}}</strong> has shared read-only MCP access to the project
        <strong>{{projectName}}</strong> with you.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can connect any MCP-compatible AI agent to this project using the credentials below.
        No account required.
      </p>

      <div class="key-box">
        <p><strong>Your API Key</strong> — keep this private, do not forward this email</p>
        <code class="code">{{apiKey}}</code>
        <p class="warning">⚠ This key grants read-only access to {{projectName}}. It will not be shown again.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h3>MCP Server Details</h3>
        <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:13px;color:#555;">Endpoint URL</p>
        <code class="code">{{mcpUrl}}</code>
        <p style="margin:12px 0 6px;font-size:13px;color:#555;">Project ID</p>
        <code class="code">{{projectId}}</code>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h3>Configure your AI agent</h3>

        <h4>Claude Desktop</h4>
        <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:13px;color:#555;">
          Add the following to your <code style="background:#eee;padding:2px 5px;border-radius:3px;">claude_desktop_config.json</code>:
        </p>
        <code class="code">{{snippets.claudeDesktop}}</code>

        <h4>Cursor</h4>
        <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:13px;color:#555;">
          Add the following to your Cursor MCP settings:
        </p>
        <code class="code">{{snippets.cursor}}</code>
      </div>

      <p>
        To revoke this access at any time, the project admin can delete the token from the
        project's API token settings.
      </p>

      <p>If you weren't expecting this, you can safely ignore this email — no action is required.</p>

      <p>— The emergent memory team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        MCP endpoint: <a href="{{mcpUrl}}">{{mcpUrl}}</a><br>
        Sent from emergent memory · <a href="https://emergent.memory">emergent.memory</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
